Runtime bundle installs these skill directories:
- `kb-compile` -> `skills/kb-compile`
- `kb-ingest` -> `skills/kb-ingest`
- `kb-init` -> `skills/kb-init`
- `kb-query` -> `skills/kb-query`
- `kb-render` -> `skills/kb-render`
- `kb-review` -> `skills/kb-review`
- `obsidian-notes-karpathy` -> `skills/obsidian-notes-karpathy`
Repo-only dev assets stay outside the installed runtime bundle:
- `evals/skills/obsidian-notes-karpathy`
- `target/`, `.runtime-evals/`, and other generated workspaces
